description: Smooth, subtle citrus notes and floral aroma.
Orange zest, marmalade, and grapefruit. Floral and spicy.
Funky and dry. Pineapple, leather, and ripe peach.
Crackery sweetness balanced with hops, floral and herbal notes that finish with a subtle citrus. Step mashed and hopped with Nobles.
Rich malt flavor with notes of toasted caramel, dark fruit, and chocolate.
Pineapple, peach rings, bubblegum, strawberry and citrus.
hops: Estate Grown Comet, Vic Secret, Galaxy

description: Caramel, orange, dark chocolate and vanilla. Conditioned on cracked Madagascar vanilla beans and Cocoa nibs.
Roasted chestnut, chocolate and raisin. Ruby hue and a hint of noble hops.
